  1747                                  ; create Buffer Descriptor List
  1748                                  ;
  1749                                  ; A buffer descriptor list is a list of pointers and control bits that the
  1750                                  ; DMA engine uses to know where to get the .wav data and how to play it.
  1751                                  ;
  1752                                  ; I set it up to use only 2 buffers of .wav data, and whenever 1 buffer is
